title: Freddy "Tavarish" Hernandez
description:
Freddy is one of the biggest automotive YouTubers. He buys broken or wrecked exotics, movie cars, and weird projects, and brings them back to life.

 

See all his crazy builds here: https://www.youtube.com/user/tavarish
